==Mandarin==

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: yī rì wéi shī, zhōng shēn wéi fù

===Proverb===
'''[[一]][[日]][[为]][[师]],[[终身]][[为]][[父]]'''

# Even if someone is your teacher for only a day, you should regard him like your father for the rest of your life.

===Alternate forms===
[[一日為師，終身為父]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

